text.tspan: One of our spies interviewed a random
kid in the streets, he asked him what
should he be when he grows up, and the
guy asked "I wanna be a drummer" So
he then brang him to Yoko Jonn's lab,
as he was our leading scientist. They
used one of his machines, and then
looking creature, he grew three hands
in his body, and thus he is now named
as Klap, and is now contained.
